工业相机SDK 日志服务安装、卸载使用说明。
===========================================================================

日志服务安装和卸载：
===========================================================================
（1）安装完客户端后，日志服务目录在/opt/(软件名)/logserver路径下，默认日志路径在/var/log/(软件名)/MvSdkLog路径下
（2）日志服务安装：首先进入/opt/(软件名)/logserver路径下，执行sudo ./InstallServer.sh 或者 sudo bash ./InstallServer.sh。
（3）日志服务卸载：首先进入/opt/(软件名)/logserver路径下，执行sudo ./RemoveServer.sh 或者 sudo bash ./RemoveServer.sh。
===========================================================================
	
查看是否安装成功方法：
===========================================================================
执行ps -aux | grep MvLogServer命令，查看是否该进程，或者打开客户端日志查看工具是否有日志显示：





Instructions for installing and uninstalling logserver for industrial cameras SDK.
===========================================================================

Logserver installation and uninstallation:
===========================================================================
（1）After installing client software, install the logerver in the/opt/(Software)/logserver path, SDK log path is /var/log/(Software)/MvSdkLog
（2）Logserver installation: First, enter the /opt/(Software)/logserver path and execute "sudo ./InstallServer.sh or sudo bash ./InstallServer.sh" command.
（3）Logserver Uninstallation: Enter the /opt/(Software)/logserver path and execute "sudo ./RemoveServer.sh or sudo bash ./RemoveServer.sh" command.
===========================================================================
	
To check whether the installation was successful:
===========================================================================
Execute the ps -aux | grep MvLogServer check whether the MvLogServer process exist.

